description:
Theo talks about why he thinks Cory Sandhagen actually beat T.J Dillashaw, how a bad batch of laundry detergent can ruin your whole week and takes suggestions from callers on what their “Last Words” would be. Theo also checks in with a single mom who's living that barefoot summer camp life in Canada with her four little ones.
